                media -- it is simply not my thing. Instead, I find my energy
                outdoors: hiking the trails around the Kogelberg Biosphere,
                walking on the beach, or simply being present in the remarkable
                natural beauty that surrounds Kleinmond.
              </p>
              <p>
                I am also a keen sports fan and, when the day winds down, you
                will likely find me unwinding with a game on the PS5. These
                quieter pursuits balance the intensity that comes with leading
                engineering teams across multiple time zones.
